
Overview of noun cream

The noun cream has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (2) cream, pick -- (the best people or things in a group; "the cream of England's young men were killed in the Great War")
2. cream -- (the part of milk containing the butterfat)
3. cream, ointment, emollient -- (toiletry consisting of any of various substances in the form of a thick liquid that have a soothing and moisturizing effect when applied to the skin)

